IN	3/4 pound tomatoes (about 2 medium), seeded and finely diced (1 1/2 cups)
IN	1/3 cup chopped cilantro
IN	1/4 cup finely chopped white onion
IN	1 small fresh jalape√±o or serrano chile, finely chopped, including seeds, or more to taste
IN	1 tablespoon freshly squeezed lime juice, or more to taste
IN	1/2 teaspoon fine salt, or 1 teaspoon kosher salt
PR	Mix all the ingredients together in a bowl. Season to taste with additional chile, lime juice, and salt.
PR	This salsa keeps in the refrigerator for up to one day. Before you serve it, stir it well and drain any excess liquid that has accumulated in the bowl.
